name: CORGIBOT
description: People create their metal analogs. People want these analogs to be able to think, to create, to love, as in "WALL-E" and to live according to all human laws. To act according to those laws is to be happy. And what's happiness without four-legged fluffy guys? Let's not deprive robots of simple (non)human happiness and create corgibots for them! Do you hear that synthy "woof"?
